	bool "MTK_KXTJ2_1009_NEW for Mediatek package"
	default n
	help
	Say Y here if you have MTK_KXTJ2_1009_NEW accelerometer sensor CUSTOM_KERNEL_SENSORHUB.

	If unsure, say N.

	To compile this dirver as a module, choose M here: the
